*   ## **_JON MOXLEY RETURNS TO AEW FOR THE FIRST TIME SINCE FORBIDDEN FOOR AND HES ROCKING HIS DEATH RIDER THEME SONG_**
    

"ITS GONNA TAKE SOME TIME FOR EVERYONE TO WRAP THEIR HEADS AROUND THIS... LOOK AT ME WHEN I'M TALKING TO YOU.

THIS NOT YOUR COMPANY ANYMORE."

\- An unhinged "DEATH RIDER" Jon Moxley talking to Tony Shiavonne... but it seems he's actually talking to Tony Khan or the Elite.

Jon Moxley was also looking to have a conversation with Darby Allin. It appears the next big main event storyline is about to begin in AEW

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7942584e-1d9e-4924-88cc-7b17c2360c82/Screenshot_20240828_171028.jpg?format=original)

