*   ## **_HANGMAN ADAM PAGE DEF. TOMOHIRO ISHII_**
    

Absolute hard hitting battle. Excellent brawl.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/16946a7f-bc9c-4f15-b396-9eecbe4eee9d/20240828_173345.jpg?format=original)

Swerve Strickland says he could attack Hangman right now but he wants to meet him eye to eye, man to man

Because Swerve Strickland feels SORRY for Hangman. Hangman can't seem to win ANYTHING. He lost the Owen Cup, he lost the Casino Gauntlet because he's so obsessed with Swerve.

Meanwhile Swerve has become the ace of company and a world champion. Swerve says Hangman Page has become a petulant child.

Hangman tells Swerve hes nothing but a piece of sh\*t who's never been able to beat him on his own. Because Swerve is just not as good as Hangman.

Swerve challenges Hangman to a Cage match.

But he's not done. He wants Hangman to know that hes been to his house AGAIN. But this time he just watched.

Swerve watched Hangman take care of his family like a MAN. A real cowboy. This is what Swerve wants from Hangman again.

Hangman walks away.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/46ab6b22-2f4a-4ded-9851-4ecde6881315/20240828_175133.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_JAMIE HAYTER DEF. HARLEY CAMERON_**
    

Post match, SARAYA runs away from Hayter

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cb018ca1-2d0b-48f6-ad5f-26bd95435559/20240828_180150.jpg?format=original)

"Ruining your life is my life... Ruining your life my FET\*SH."

Daniel Garcia to MJF

MJF comes out and denounces his American citizenship because the American people weren't there to help him defeat Ospreay.

MJF talks about how his ring was stolen and how his neck is injured. He says he'll get Ospreay some day but if he ever sees Daniel Garcia again....

Of course Garcia attacks and a massive brawl breaks out. Garcia desperately tries to piledrive MJF off the turnbuckle but officials won't allow it.

Garcia reveals he's the one who stole the Dynamite Diamond Ring. He pawned it to get a flight to London to ruin MJF's life.

MJF vs Daniel Garcia is on for AEW ALL OUT!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d45462e9-27ed-4deb-b57b-a4c7f3255c41/20240828_180131.jpg?format=original)

