RICOCHET officially using the VERTIGO as his finisher in AEW to defeat Kyle Fletcher.

Ospreay comes out to confront Ricochet but he's CLEARLY forgotten about PAC and that's a mistake. PAC attacks.

PAC sends a message to Will Ospreay and welcomes Ricochet to AEW by telling him to get to the back of the line!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a34a78ae-3b14-4ada-832b-97936762438b/20240828_190443.jpg?format=original)

Marina Shafir joins Jon Moxley

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/43196423-1190-4384-8fdf-2482aa013866/20240828_191105.jpg?format=original)

Bryan Danielson says he’s not going to retire as AEW Champion, but if he loses the title, his full-time career is going to end.

He says he'll take on anyone at All Out, first come first serve. Then Jack Perry appears on screen to distract Bryan by reminding him that Perry is the last person to pin him.

Perry tells Bryan his future is behind him now... then he attacks Bryan from behind.

It appears Jack Perry vs Bryan Danielson for the AEW World Championship at All Out

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b96c08de-760f-4df2-85a1-3f7f3f2d9f94/20240828_190955.jpg?format=original)